TITLE: Rendering Meta Tags with React Components
DESCRIPTION: Example using renderMetaTags() function to generate React meta and link elements compatible with libraries like react-helmet. The function converts DatoCMS meta tag data into React components.
SOURCE: https://github.com/datocms/react-datocms/blob/master/docs/meta-tags.md#2025-04-17_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: jsx
CODE:
```
import React from 'react';
import { renderMetaTags } from 'react-datocms';

function Page({ data }) {
  return (
    <div>
      <Helmet>
        {renderMetaTags([...data.page.seo, ...data.site.favicon])}
      </Helmet>
    </div>
  );
}
```

